---
title: Seared Beef Rump & Onion Gravy with Mash & Roasted Root Veggies
description: Long after you finish this dinner of steak and three veg, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple addition of a luscious onion gravy. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease on life.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67108bc45e99f1b6964358ac-c74fd58a.jpeg
